casebody.data:
Andrea IRWIN, AS NEXT FRIEND OF E.I., a minor, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
COVENANT MEDICAL CENTER, INC., d/b/a Covenant Healthcare, Defendant-Appellee,
and
Deborah L. Russell, M.D., Radha Cherukuri, M.D., Daniel J. Wechter, M.D., and Maternal-Fetal Medicine, P.C., Defendants. SC: 159014
COA: 338395 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 28, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the November 1, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
